{"tid":1516543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[癡線作者] 點擊此處與地方的穴蛾展開真誠對話","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:16.000Z","uid":82688,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3beacdbbfeec34c0293a644952b9f8ad4fa963cf","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"月黑如元朗、風高如葵芳之夜，禮_府內迴蕩著「咯啦咯啦」的聲響。在昏黃的燈光映照下，好打得的穴蛾面上彷似塗上了狂戰士的戰紋，像是失心瘋般邊咬牙切齒邊重複著：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「點解你地全部人都唔明」</span></span></strong><br />\n在她的世界裡，世人根本不懂得欣賞她亮麗的修辭，能把單單「撤回」二字，包裝成「暫緩」和「壽終正寢」實在把語言藝術耍得登峰造極。<br />\n倏忽「啪」的一聲，就如王毅的大喝一聲，房門被打開了，映入眼簾的竟然是一名白衣男子。。。"},{"pid":"4769b91ead22b609f516e1752e91a5a0b74bffc2","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d0f9b4df9574f4db8ecd49212ddfe565e71bc85c","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"05254619fdbda5b71af2b1a1db30ccee4871b519","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"51e0d56caa9c0cbfdf415a6f753c2965956dd7b5","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f5cdc4418af1b11e9eef5be46bd047b97f0550ab","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f7420ccdfd0e2d796f81cb191dba87388e3a5d30","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:06:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7c97efb45c67912ff3f27b02894a6d264866a2db","tid":1516543,"uid":82688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15